# Wharton Hockey Project (Round 1)

This github repository contains the notebooks used for exploratory analysis, feature engineering, modeling, and visualizations.

## Contents

### 1) `HockeyEDA`
- Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA) as well as our power ranking. 
- Creates initial aggregated tables with feature engineering variables that we use in later notebooks. 

### 2) `hockeyModelMAIN`
  - Main Round 1 prediction model notebook 

### 3) `Offense1v2Disp`
  - Notebook for our creating offensive team disparity (first line vs second line)

### 4) HockeyVisualizations
  - Notebook for visualizing the correlation between power ranking and offensive team disparity. 
